title: 185. Andy & DJ CTI: CNN Suspends Chris Cuomo, Dr. Oz Running For Senate & Dr. Evil
itunes:title: 185. Andy & DJ CTI: CNN Suspends Chris Cuomo, Dr. Oz Running For Senate & Dr. Evil
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ talk about CNN suspending Chris Cuomo after new documents revealed he helped his brother former NY Gov. Andrew Cuomo who was facing sexual harassment charges, Dr. Oz's announcement to run as a Republican for the open U.S. Senate seat in Pennsylvania and Fauci's NIH funding lethal medical experiments on Orphans with AIDS in NY City.
